         <abstract>
            <p>The complete solution in (n, y&lt;sub&gt;1&lt;/sub&gt;, y&lt;sub&gt;2&lt;/sub&gt;) ∈ Z&lt;sup&gt;3&lt;/sup&gt; of the Diophantine equation b&lt;sub&gt;n&lt;/sub&gt; = ± 2&lt;sup&gt;y&lt;sub&gt;1&lt;/sub&gt;&lt;/sup&gt; 3&lt;sup&gt;y&lt;sub&gt;2&lt;/sub&gt;&lt;/sup&gt; is given, where (b&lt;sub&gt;n&lt;/sub&gt;)&lt;sub&gt;n ∈ Z&lt;/sub&gt; is Berstel's recurrence sequence defined by b&lt;sub&gt;0&lt;/sub&gt; = b&lt;sub&gt;1&lt;/sub&gt; = 0, b&lt;sub&gt;2&lt;/sub&gt; = 1, b&lt;sub&gt;n + 3&lt;/sub&gt; = 2b&lt;sub&gt;n + 2&lt;/sub&gt; - 4b&lt;sub&gt;n + 1&lt;/sub&gt; + 4b&lt;sub&gt;n&lt;/sub&gt;.</p>
          </abstract>
